title: For Sale:     1 of 17 View Larger Images                                  NORINCO SKS 30, SKS-D, ALL MATCHING, USES AK47
postcontent:
These rifles are commonly referred to as “SKS-D” rifles but it’s actually a very uncommon “SKS 30” rifle, NOT A CONVERSION. The SKS 30 rifles were factory built to accept AK 47 magazines and were imported to the US in this configuration. The “SKS D” rifles were regular Chinese SKS56 rifles that were converted to accept AK mags by Midwest Ordnance in Nebraska. The SKS 30 rifles are much less common, with less than 7k ever imported, and a great addition to any SKS collection.
The SKS 30 rifles also feature a quick detachable folding bayonet that can be completely removed from the rifle. This is a feature unique to SKS 30 rifles.Shipping is accepted... shipping fee cost for $35
